text: Mikhaylovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Krasnovoskhodsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 211 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 95 km from Iglino, 10 km from Krasny Voskhod. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Mikhaylovka, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
